We are so grateful for all the teachers who have impacted our lives and the lives of our players! We have always been in awe of you, but especially now. THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING! Happy Teacher Appreciation Week! - South Middleton School District, Carlisle Area School District, Mount Holly Springs Elementary School;

